flowRoot.flowPara: DataLad can obtain required subdataset content on demand. Only content elements actually required for an analysis are present. Directory structure is expanded recursively as needed.
Required (3rd-party) code repositories can be referenced as subdatasets just like datasets with data files. Repository state is unambiguous version record.
